snippet.title: Space Shooter Godot Game Template
snippet.description:
Use this Game Template made in Godot to create your own Space Shooter Game. Completely Free assets and code.

Get it here: https://ansimuz.itch.io/warped-space-shooter

If you like my work consider supporting it on Patreon and get access to  a growing library of Pixel Art Files :  https://www.patreon.com/ansimuz

Find me at:
SHOP: https://ansimuz.itch.io/
